Knife Fight - Season 3, Episode 11


Quarterfinals: Cuttlefish

First round champs Edi Frauneder and Franklin Becker square off in a quarterfinal match to see who will advance to the semi-finals, as they cook with cuttlefish, chocolate and chicken livers.




Knife Fight - Season 3, Episode 12


Quarterfinals: Suckling Pig

n tonight's quarterfinal match up, New York's famous Italian chef, Joey Campanaro, is back to compete against James Beard Award winner Tony Maws. They'll have to impress judges Naomi Pomeroy and Kris Morningstar to move onto the semifinals.




Original Air Date: 30-Jun-2015
